gomodel:SYNGO_3090  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Fig.1: \"ROR2 protein is located in peri-synaptic clusters in cultured hippocampal neurons\"\n\nFig.2: \"ROR2 protein is located in dendritic protrusions in cultured hippocampal neurons\". Experimental description: - \" Primary cultures of hippocampal neurons were prepared according to the protocol described by Brewer et al. (1993). Briefly, hippocampus of 18-d-old Sprague-Dawley rat embryos were dissected ...\"\n- Overexpressed ROR2 is of mouse species: \"The expression vectors pcDNA3-mROR2wt-FLAG, pcDNA3-mROR2ΔCRD-FLAG, pcDNA3-mROR2KD-FLAG and pcDNA3-mROR2ΔCt-FLAG, w...\"" ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
        dc:contributor    "https://orcid.org/0000-0003-0593-3443" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2514-0216" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2286-1587" ;
        dc:date           "2018-04-09" ;
